# Service Layer

The services layer provides integrations with external systems and handles data storage and retrieval operations.

## Vector Database Services

- [milvus_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/milvus_service.py): Implements the Milvus vector database integration for storing and retrieving document embeddings.
- [embedding_storage_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/embedding_storage_service.py): Provides a higher-level interface for managing embedded documents.

## AI Model Services

- [watsonx_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/watsonx_service.py): Implements the integration with IBM Watsonx foundation models for text generation.
- [litellm_watsonx_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/litellm_watsonx_service.py): Provides LiteLLM compatibility for Watsonx models.

## Storage and Caching

- [cos_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/cos_service.py): Implements IBM Cloud Object Storage integration for document storage.
- [cache_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/cache_service.py): Provides caching functionality to improve performance.

## Web Search

- [discovery_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/discovery_service.py): Implements IBM Watson Discovery integration for web search capabilities.

## Maintenance

- [cleanup_service.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/services/cleanup_service.py): Provides utilities for cleaning up temporary files and resources.

